+### Overall workflow status
+
+| Status        | Meaning                                                              |
+|---------------|----------------------------------------------------------------------|
+| `succeeded`   | Every step that ran succeeded (any number of `skipped` is fine).     |
+| `failed`      | No step that ran succeeded — every non-skipped step failed/timed-out/was cancelled. |
+| `partial`     | A mix: at least one step succeeded **and** at least one failed/timed-out/was cancelled. |
+| `interrupted` | Run was stopped via SIGINT/SIGTERM (takes precedence).               |
+
 ### Interrupting a run (Ctrl+C)
 
